author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description: Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! Computers are something I have always loved and with that so has gaming, now a piece of technology threatens to push that back to the dark ages for the foreseeable future. RAM prices have gone through the roof and now some of the biggest sellers are leaving the market to cater to AI bros. Thanks for watching!
title: Things Have Gotten So Bad Lately...
